h3. Status
A dedicated team is working on providing a solution as soon as possible.

h3. Workaround
Automatic fixing is in place that will recover the site when the problem is detected by automated alerts.
If unsure or for information, contact [Cloud Support|https://support.atlassian.com] for help mentioning this bug.
